snippet.title: Diana and Barbie Party
snippet.description:
Diana organized a Barbie party. Only Barbie Dolls and girls can go there. The boy Roma wanted to go to the party, and changed into a Barbie girl. Diana drove the boy from the party, but then he came back and looked like Ken. Funny video for kids
